101st Ave., at the S.W. corner of Van Wyck Boulevard, showing the Dunton Hotel, operated or owned by August Williams in 1922. In 1923 Chas. Richter acquired it and rented it. It was no longer in
existence in 1934.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
